<% title "Written Boards" %>

<h1> <%= yield(:title) %> <br>
<span style="font-size: 0.5em"> part 1  / BASIC and ADVANCED exams </span></h1>

<div class='exams'>
  <p>
    The ABA has phased out the traditional <%= external_link_to *@part1 %> written exam. 
    Residents graduating after June 30, 2016 now take the <%= external_link_to *@staged %>.
  </p>
  
  <p>
    Median pass rate for first time takers of the Part 1 exam (2009-2015) was 88% 
  </p>
  
  <p>  
    The <%= external_link_to *@basic %> exam is offered twice a year: June and November. To be eligible for the June exam, one must have completed 6 months of CA-1 training by March 31. 
  </p>
  
  <div class="center">
      <%= image_tag("BasicStats.png") %>
  </div>
  <br>
  <p>
    The first <%= external_link_to *@advanced %> exam was administered in July 2016. Starting in 2017, it will be offered twice a year: January and July. To be eligible for the July exam, one must have completed 6 months of CA-3 training by March 31. 
  </p>

  <p>
    BASIC/ADVANCED exam <%= external_link_to *@aba_content_outline %>.
  </p>
  
  <p>
    <%= external_link_to *@basicq %> and <%= external_link_to *@advancedq %> sample questions.
  </p>
  
  <p>
    2013 - 2016 <%= external_link_to *@gaps %> reports.
  </p>

  <p>
  The released <%= external_link_to *@old_aba_exams %>, categorized into BASIC/ADVANCED may be searched below.
  K-type questions have been eliminated. 
  </p>

  <div class="center">
    <form accept-charset="UTF-8" action="/questions" method="get" name="commit" class="form-inline">
      
      <div class="row">   
        <div class="checkbox">
          Stems              <%= check_box_tag 'stems_checkbox',   '1', true %><br/>
          Answer Choices     <%= check_box_tag 'choices_checkbox', '1', true %>
        </div>
      
        <div class="form-group">
          <input type="search" name="search" class="input-large" id="search" placeholder="Search">
        </div>
      
        <div class="checkbox">
          <div class="shufflebox">
            <%= check_box_tag 'shuffle_checkbox', '1', true %> Shuffle
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    
        <br><br>
      
      <div class="row"> 
        <select class="form-control" name="exam" id="exam">
          <option value="4">BASIC & ADVANCED</option>
          <option value="1">BASIC</option>
          <option value="2">ADVANCED</option>
          <option value="3">Uncategorized</option>
        </select>

        <select class="form-control" name="topic_id" id="topic_id">
          <option value="11">All Topics</option>
          <option value="1">Equipment & Physics</option>
          <option value="2">Respiratory & Critical Care</option>
          <option value="3">Pharmacology & Pharmacokinetics</option>
          <option value="4">Transfusions & Fluids</option>
          <option value="5">General</option>
          <option value="6">Pediatric</option>
          <option value="7">OB</option>
          <option value="8">Neuro</option>
          <option value="9">Cardiac</option>
          <option value="10">Regional & Pain</option>
        </select> 
      </div>    
    
      <div class="row">
        <button type="submit" style="margin:1em" class="btn btn-danger btn-lg">Search the Questions</button>
        <%= link_to "10 Random Questions", "/questions/random", class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg" %>
      </div>
    </form>
  
    <p class="disclaimer">
      &copy; Joint Council on In-Training Examinations, American Board of
      Anesthesiology, American Society of Anesthesiologists
    </p>
    <br><br>
  </div>  

  <p>
    An extensive list of keywords can be found at <%= external_link_to *@open_anesthesia_keywords %>
  </p>
  
  <p>
    The University of Kentucky department of anesthesia <%= external_link_to *@kentucky_keywords %>
  </p>
  
  <p>
    My own anesthesia math review <%= external_link_to "Problem Set", @mathps %> and <%= external_link_to "Solutions", @mathsol %>
  </p>
  
  <p>
    Board review <%= external_link_to "books", category_resources_path("Written Board") %>
  </p>

  <p>
    Information about the British <%= external_link_to "FRCA examination", @frca %> and a site devoted to it 
    from the <%= external_link_to "Northern Ireland School of Anaesthesia", @nisoa %>
  </p>

  <p>
  Discussion threads at <%= link_to_sdn_forum %> 
  </p>
  
  <ul>
    <%= render partial: 'site', collection: @study_strategy %>
  </ul>
  
  <br>
    
  <p> Written board commercial prep courses:</p>
  
  <p class="disclaimer">
    I don't have any experience with these products and do not endorse any
    particular product
  </p>
  
  <ul>
    <%= render partial: 'site', collection: @commercial_courses %>
  </ul>
  
</div>
